{"tid":2447300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府檢討推「疫苗假」讓民眾安心接種疫苗及避免強制要求接種疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-15T06:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T06:20:11.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ae872883561e8452b4ef104564042b326d4051e6","tid":2447300,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:06:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">香港就一味迫你打，甚至屌鳩你點解唔打</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580662-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580662-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=7d9fcaff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580662-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=84403af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580662-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日本行政改革擔當大臣河野太郎昨日提出，為了讓民眾安心接種新冠疫苗，有意推動企業讓員工放「疫苗假」。<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官加藤勝信今日上午在記者會說，如何確保工作的民眾接種，以及一旦出現副作用的問題，政府考量不同情況，以政府立場，讓民眾安心接種疫苗的環境很重要，但會留意避免接種疫苗變成強制。</strong><br />\n<br />\n日本首批接種疫苗為醫護人員，預計下月中起為65歲以上人士打針，之後再逐步擴大，最後讓一般民眾接種。"},{"pid":"fad98ffd4f3d3b622a5def66a7ce11fc10f3dc20","tid":2447300,"uid":63157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"相信日本人都係會照返工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbc438c48fda17df082caae88d45368276132d6","tid":2447300,"uid":393145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:10:25.000Z","msg":"香港政府:<br />\n''呼籲''企業...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672a4066a3241f48b97114d4b89d5f8e28637c1f","tid":2447300,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"香港打完死撚左都可以懶9 個死者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee6b5a868a6bac46a9dadab027031553aaba147","tid":2447300,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"放幾多日先？癱咗係咪包一世"},{"pid":"c7a8d1b8d54a6fba40534b34ca818a98233f3816","tid":2447300,"uid":12796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:20:11.000Z","msg":"某國：推「假疫苗」"}]}